description-en_US-print:
The network ready MB461 is the ideal choice for small businesses or workgroups requiring print, copy and scan functionality. This high performance all-in-one printer delivers an impressive 33ppm mono print speed, flexible media handling and automatic duplex printing as standard to bring added functionality and superior printing to your workplace. And with an intuitive, easy to use operator panel, comprehensive scanning functionality and a Reversing Automatic Document Feeder (RADF), the MB461 will allow you to work efficiently with both single and double sided documents. Low running costs consolidate the savings made from a low purchase price and a free 3 year onsite warranty to make the MB461 a very attractive option for the budget conscious business.

<b>Fast, r eliable and easy to use</b>
- Print speeds of 33ppm for time critical print jobs;
- Built on tried and tested, award winning digital LED technology;
- Ideal for use by a wide range of organisations thanks to its flexible media handling, from labels to spreadsheets, invoices, proposals, forms, technical drawings and more;
- Perfect for businesses that require fast mono printing with the added functionality of copying and colour scanning.

<b>Great features to improve workplace productivity</b>
The MB461 is packed full of outstanding standard features, including:
- 50-sheet RADF enabling you to copy and scan two sided documents;
- Front facing USB port enabling you to directly print from a USB stick;
- Overlay function enables you to save logos or forms in the MFP memory, for re-use in other documents;
- Compatible with mobile printing applications allowing you to print directly from your mobile device over wireless networks.

<b>Looking after the environment</b>
The MB461 is one of the most environmentally conscious A4 mono MFPs on the market, incorporating a wide range of features to help your organisation reduce its energy consumption, impact on the environment and ongoing costs.:

- Reduced energy usage through combining several devices in one;
- Advanced LED technology;
- Eco and Deep Sleep modes;
- Reduced toner usage with a Toner Save function, Duplex printing and advanced copying functionality that helps to reduce the amount you print.
